               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18391216-name-286" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18391216-name-286" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391216-name-286" type="surname" value="FRESHWATER"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391216-name-286" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>MARY FRESHWATER</persName>
                  </hi>. I am the wife of William Freshwater. We keep a chandler's shop in Cromer-street. On the 11th of December the prisoner came into the shop and asked for charity—I said I could not relieve him, but I went to the till with the intention of giving him 1<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—in going there I missed this bacon—I said, "You have taken some bacon, have you not?"—he said, "Yes, I have, and I will give it you again"—I went to call my neighbour, and the prisoner was gone with the bacon—I did not see him again till he was in custody.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Did I offer it you again? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> Yes—you must have taken it from the counter.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18391216-name-287" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18391216-name-287" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391216-name-287" type="surname" value="WILLIAMS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18391216-name-287" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY WILLIAMS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant E</hi> 8.) I heard a cry of "Stop thief," and met the prisoner running, calling "Stop thief" himself—I asked what was the matter—he said, a man had stolen a piece of meat and run that way—knowing that no one bad passed me, I said, "I must take you and search you"—I found this bacon in his pocket—I found 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. on him, also, a number of penny loaves, and other things.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi>. I said, if I had got her bacon it was unknown to me—it was given me by a gentleman outside the shop.</p>
